article.description: — Antonio Daye Jr. had 19 points as Fordham romped past Akron 63-43 in the Gulf Coast Showcase on Monday night.
article.headline: Daye scores 19 to carry Fordham past Akron 63-43
article.linkText: Daye scores 19 to carry Fordham past Akron 63-43
article.story: ESTERO, Fla. -- — Antonio Daye Jr. had 19 points as Fordham romped past Akron 63-43 in the Gulf Coast Showcase on Monday night. Daye made 8 of 10 free throws. Darius Quisenberry had 17 points for Fordham (3-2). Kyle Rose added seven rebounds and Antrell Charlton had seven rebounds. Enrique Freeman had 11 rebounds for the Zips (2-2). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
